headline: Humana Partners to Expand Mental Health Education for Louisville’s Next Generation
summary: LOUISVILLE, Ky., October 23, 2025--Following World Mental Health Day, the Humana Foundation – the philanthropic arm of Humana Inc. for the past 44 years – along with Jewish Heritage Fund and the University of Louisville’s Christina Lee Brown Envirome Institute, announced the grand opening of the new "Health and Well-being Center" at Junior Achievement (JA) Finance Park of Kentucky. The milestone was marked with a ribbon-cutting ceremony at the Park.
